synopsis.text: Pichu's Brother Pikachu is in grave danger, and it's up to a group of brave Pokémon to come to the rescue! But this isn't your typical Pokémon adventure - the leader of the group is a human who has mysteriously transformed into a Squirtle! With the ability to understand and communicate with other Pokémon, this young person must navigate a world filled with natural disasters and team up with Charmander and Chikorita to form "Team Go-Getters." Their mission is clear: find and save Pikachu before the rival group, "Team Meanies," can get their hands on him. Will our hero and their new friends be able to overcome the challenges that lie ahead and rescue Pikachu in time? Join Team Go-Getters on their thrilling journey and find out!
